summary: TWO OF FOUR WHEELS ON THIS VEHICLE WERE FOUND TO BE CRACKED ON THE INBOARD FLANGE/BEAD SEAT AREA.  THESE CRACKS WERE FOUND DURING A ROUTINE SERVICE FOR TIRE ROTATION.
